title: Glenn Frey - Solo Collection (1995) [FLAC]
description:
After the Eagles disbanded, Glenn Frey found solo success in the 1980s, especially with two No. 2 hits: the soundtrack songs "The Heat Is On" (from Beverly Hills Cop) and "You Belong to the City" (from the television series Miami Vice), the soundtrack of which stayed on top of the U.S. album charts for 11 weeks in 1985.

Solo Collection is a greatest hits album of Glenn Freys solo career, released in 1995.
